		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_3_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} promotes the practice of Counting Coup!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_4_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} places increased importance on the ancient burial sites of his people.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_5_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} creates a nigh-uncrackable code for military use!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_6_S">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} receives a Unique Event for {1_CivShortDescription}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_NOTIFICATION_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>{3_PlayerName} combats climate change by giving over state funding and research to solar technology.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Be Careful With Greatness</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_HELP">
			<Text>Strong and cunning Chief, the elders are assembled around the Great Fire. The ritual is awaits once more.[NEWLINE]Spirits guide you, Poctallo.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Receive a Great Person of your choice.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Incorporation of [ICON_RES_BISON] Bison into our fundamental culture boosts their [ICON_CULTURE] Culture, [ICON_PEACE] Faith, [ICON_GOLD] Gold and [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points by +1.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Melee and Gun Units gain the Counting Coup promotion: earning [ICON_CULTURE] Culture on kill, and increasing experience gains by 25%.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>Invest {1_YieldCost} in our funerary rites, allowing Encampments to generate +1 [ICON_PEACE] Faith and +1 [ICON_GOLDEN_AGE] Golden Age Points.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_HELP_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>Spend {1_YieldCost} to create an extremely resilient code that grants the Sentry Promotion to all eligible Units.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_HELP_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>Utilise {1_YieldCost} to develop ultra-low cost solar panels, receiving a Solar Plant in all Cities.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>*A figure is seen standing in the smoke, reaching out toward you*[NEWLINE]The life of a Great Man is in danger! Prepare the horses, we go to find them, immediately.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>*Through the fire and flames a small calf grows into a mighty beast, who is felled and then disperses into many objects around the camp*[NEWLINE]The spirits are clear, our symbiosis with the Bison must be strengthened still!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>*A great black figure stoops and spins trying to catch a dancing ember before falling back into darkness*[NEWLINE]Our warriors have pleased our ancestors, let it be known that the practise of Counting Coup shall no longer be looked down upon by this council!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>*The figure of a crying woman is observed by a host of floating spectres*[NEWLINE]The spirits are restless; our offerings are not reaching them. We must reaffirm the holiness of our burial grounds.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_5">
			<Text>*Two smokey figures converse while a third shadow can be seen trying to listen in*[NEWLINE]In our time of need we are guided by our ancestors! What we have never realised is a strength has the power to defeat our enemies!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_SHOSHONE_UE_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_6">
			<Text>*A dusky river evaporates into a barren field, then the burst of the fire leaves you blind for a few moments*[NEWLINE]The spirits cry out. This world is dying. We must act if we are to secure the future for our children.</Text>
		</Row>

		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PROMOTION_UE_COUNTING_COUP">
			<Text>Counting Coup</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_PROMOTION_UE_COUNTING_COUP_HELP">
			<Text>Receive [ICON_CULTURE] Culture from victories, and earn 25% more experience from battle.</Text>
		</Row>
	</Language_en_US>
</GameData>